{
  "logNo": "110190710759",
  "title": "바른자세는 척추건강의 시작 [사당동 추나교정한의원 이수한의원]",
  "addDate": "2014. 5. 13.",
  "categoryNo": "14",
  "parentCategoryNo": "7",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110190710759",
  "html_size": 197745,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110190710759\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110190710759\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><div class=\"view\" style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'><!--StartFragment--><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (&lt;!==[if gte vml 1]&gt;) --><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">척추관절 및 근골격계 질환의 예방은</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">바른자세에서 시작됩니다. </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">과거와 달리 앉아서 생활하는 시간이 길기 때문에</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">기립, 보행시의 자세보다는 </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">앉아있을 때의 자세를 더욱 신경써야 합니다. </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">척추, 관절 및 근골격계질환(측만증, 골반틀어짐, 디스크, 무릎관절염, 오십견, 근육통, 두통,&nbsp;힘줄염, 만성 재발성 근육통 등)이 생긴 후</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">침치료, 추나치료, 약침치료 및 한약복용 등을&nbsp;통해 척추교정하고 자세교정을&nbsp;하고, 통증을 없애는&nbsp;치료를 하더라도</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">이후 바른자세를 유지하지 못한다면 다시 재발할 수 밖에 없습니다.&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&#8203;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:stroke) -->&nbsp;&nbsp;<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:formulas) -->&nbsp;&nbsp;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered --><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\"> </span><!--StartFragment--></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;<span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">앉아서 컴퓨터 작업을 할 때의</span></span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">바른 자세에</span></strong> 대한 </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">코넬대학의 보고서를 소개합니다. </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;------------</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">Workstation Design Factors</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3eb23384838b24d7.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"487\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 487px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140513_85/isuhani_1399943741659h7e4a_PNG/noname01.png\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7E0CFE7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3eb23384838b24d7.png\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\"><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span><!--StartFragment--></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; use a good chair with a dynamic chair back and sit back </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;- 좋은 의자를 사용한다. </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">2.&nbsp; top of monitor casing should be 2-3\" (5-8 cm) above eye level&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">-모니터의 상단이 작업자의 눈보다 5~8cm 높아야 한다.&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">3.&nbsp; no glare on screen, use an optical glass anti-glare filter where needed </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;-모니터가 눈부심이 있으면 안된다 (필요시 눈부심 방지 필터 사용)</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">4.&nbsp; sit at arms length from monitor </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">-모니터로부터의 거리는 내가 팔을 뻗었을 때 팔 길이 정도로 한다.&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">5.&nbsp; feet on floor or stable footrest&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">-발은 바닥에 닿게 하거나, 안정된 발판위에 놓는다.&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">6.&nbsp; use a document holder, preferably in-line with the computer screen </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">-&#8203;서류 홀더를 사용하는데, 가급적 모니터와 일치(직렬로)하는게 좋다. (모니터와 서류를 동시에 보면서 작업을 해야 할 경우 서류를 모니터와 나란히 세워서 거치할 수 있는 홀더를 사용하는게 좋다는 의미네요)</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">7.&nbsp; wrists flat and straight in relation to forearms to use keyboard/mouse/input device </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">-손목은 전완(팔뚝)과 수평, 일직선이 되게 놓일 수 있도록 키보드, 마우스 등을 배치한다&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">8.&nbsp; arms and elbows relaxed and close to body&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">-팔과 팔꿈치는 편안한 위치여야 하고 몸에 가깝게 붙이는게 좋다&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">9.&nbsp; center monitor and keyboard in front of you&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">-모니터와 키보드는&nbsp;작업자의 정면에 위치&#8203;해야 한다.</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">10.&nbsp; use a negative tilt keyboard tray  with an upper mouse platform or downward tiltable platform adjacent to keyboard </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;-마이너스 경사 키보드 트레이 (키보드가 위 그림과 같이 기울어지게 거치될 수 있는 판을 말함)와 키보드에 인접한 높낮이 조절되는 마우스 거치대를 사용한다 </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">11.&nbsp; use a stable work surface and stable (no bounce) keyboard tray </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">-책상과 키보드 거치대는 안정된 것을 사용한다 &#8203;(흔들리지 않는)</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">12.&nbsp; take frequent short breaks (microbreaks)</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">-짧은 휴식시간을 자주 갖는다. &#8203;</span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]><![endif]--></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">This Information was compiled by Cornell University, Professor Alan Hedge.</span></p></span><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">----------- </p><p class=\"바탕글\">컴퓨터 작업이 잦은 분들은 위의 내용을 잘 기억하시면 좋겠습니다. </p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>가장 중요한 것은 '좋은 의자'를 쓰는거죠 ^</strong></span>^ </p><p class=\"바탕글\">앉아있는 시간이 많기 때문에 좋은 신발, 좋은 침대, 좋은 이불을 쓰는 것 만큼이나 좋은 의자를 선택하는 것은 중요합니다. </p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">위의 내용은 작업자보다 작업환경에 더 주안점을 둔 정보입니다. </p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">작업자에 더 주안점을 둔 정보는&nbsp;김연아 선수를 모델로 공부할 때의 바른 자세를 나타낸 그림이 있습니다. </p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">참고로 보도록 하죠. </p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\" class=\"바탕글\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d01a5e9849784c47.png\" width=\"436\" height=\"556\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 556px; rwidth: 436px;\" id=\"20140513_21/isuhani_1399945632224I4vYP_PNG/%B1%E8%BF%AC%BE%C6_%BE%C9%C0%BA%C0%DA%BC%BC_.png\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7E0CFE7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d01a5e9849784c47.png\"></div><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">아래의 사진들은 안좋은 자세에 대한 예시입니다. </p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">한 번 보시고</p><p class=\"바탕글\">내가 저런 자세를 잡고 있지는 않는지 되돌아 보세요. </p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\" class=\"바탕글\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a8899bd691823d7e.jpg\" width=\"183\" height=\"275\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 275px; rwidth: 183px;\" id=\"20140513_265/isuhani_1399945543403990bY_JPEG/%C0%DF%B8%F8%B5%C8_%C0%DA%BC%BC3.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7E0CFE7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a8899bd691823d7e.jpg\"></div><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">요즘 커피숍에서 노트북 사용하는 사람들이 늘었죠.</p><p class=\"바탕글\">이런 모습을 자주 봅니다. </p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\" class=\"바탕글\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/36e9be11c9bdc38a.jpg\" width=\"462\" height=\"293\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);.25px; rheight: 293.25px; rwidth: 462px;\" id=\"20140513_154/isuhani_1399945543564wgLvX_JPEG/%C0%DF%B8%F8%B5%C8_%C0%DA%BC%BC2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7E0CFE7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/36e9be11c9bdc38a.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></div><p class=\"바탕글\">짝다리 짚기</p><p class=\"바탕글\">다리꼬고 앉기</p><p class=\"바탕글\">다리 포개어 앉기</p><p class=\"바탕글\">불편하게 웅크리고 자기</p><p class=\"바탕글\">등은</p><p class=\"바탕글\">모두 나쁜 자세죠.</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\" class=\"바탕글\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/17dafcf8ed3a2852.jpg\" width=\"194\" height=\"260\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 260px; rwidth: 194px;\" id=\"20140513_224/isuhani_1399945543691EGzT7_JPEG/%C0%DF%B8%F8%B5%C8_%C0%DA%BC%BC1.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7E0CFE7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/17dafcf8ed3a2852.jpg\"></div><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">이런자세도 자주 볼 수 있죠.</p><p class=\"바탕글\">하지 말아야합니다. </p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\" class=\"바탕글\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140513_299/isuhani_1399945543772fedge_JPEG/%C0%DF%B8%F8%B5%C8_%C0%DA%BC%BC.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"306\" height=\"296\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);.6px; rheight: 296.6px; rwidth: 306px;\" id=\"20140513_299/isuhani_1399945543772fedge_JPEG/%C0%DF%B8%F8%B5%C8_%C0%DA%BC%BC.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7E0CFE7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140513_299/isuhani_1399945543772fedge_JPEG/%C0%DF%B8%F8%B5%C8_%C0%DA%BC%BC.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">모니터에 얼굴을 바짝 대고 일하는 사람 (디자인, 설계 하시는 분들 중 이런 분이 많은 것 같더군요)</p><p class=\"바탕글\">몸을 뒤로 눕히듯 앉아서 컴퓨터 하는 사람 (주로 게임방에 가보면 많이 볼 수 있습니다. ㅎㅎ)</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">이런 자세들은 모두 하지 말아야 할 나쁜 자세입니다. </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">-------------</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">척추관절 및 근골격계 질환의 예방은</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">바른자세에서 시작됩니다. </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">과거와 달리 앉아서 생활하는 시간이 길기 때문에</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">기립, 보행시의 자세보다는 </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">앉아있을 때의 자세를 더욱 신경써야 합니다. </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">척추, 관절 및 근골격계질환(측만증, 골반틀어짐, 디스크, 무릎관절염, 오십견, 근육통, 두통,&nbsp;힘줄염, 만성 재발성 근육통 등)이 생긴 후</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">침치료, 추나치료, 약침치료 및 한약복용 등을&nbsp;통해 척추교정하고 자세교정을&nbsp;하고, 통증을 없애는&nbsp;치료를 하더라도</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">이후 바른자세를 유지하지 못한다면 다시 재발할 수 밖에 없습니다. </span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">꼭 기억하세요.</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt;\"><strong>척추 건강은 바른자세에서 시작된다는걸!!!!</strong></span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">&#8203;</span></p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ac5b3b581f6330a2.png\" width=\"547\" height=\"172\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 172px; rwidth: 547px;\" id=\"20140513_118/isuhani_1399946972183Tkosc_PNG/C7D11.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7E0CFE7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ac5b3b581f6330a2.png\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140513_27/isuhani_139994697243004fWf_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"193\" height=\"48\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 48px; rwidth: 193px;\" id=\"20140513_27/isuhani_139994697243004fWf_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7E0CFE7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140513_27/isuhani_139994697243004fWf_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w3\">&#8203;</span></p>\r\n </div>\r\n </div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
